caption:
Table 1. Obviously, training on the 
target dataset brings significant performance improvement 
comparing with GoogLeNet/pool5 1024 , hard example min-
ing further brings more performance gain, while the hard 
aware method achieves the best performance. HDC + 
Contrastive-3  ?128 is much better than the traditional Hard 
+ Contrastive  ?128 as the shallow modules of the model are 
also trained by hard samples mined by shallow models. Our 
method in the last row achieves the best result comparing 
with all baselines, which verifies the effectiveness of the 
hard-aware sample mining.
